    <entry>
      <title>python小案例（四）</title>
      <link href="/posts/0/"/>
      <url>/posts/0/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<link rel="stylesheet" class="aplayer-secondary-style-marker" href="\assets\css\APlayer.min.css"><script src="\assets\js\APlayer.min.js" class="aplayer-secondary-script-marker"></script><h3 id="1-百钱百鸡"><a href="#1-百钱百鸡" class="headerlink" title="1.百钱百鸡"></a>1.百钱百鸡</h3><blockquote><p>解释：百钱百鸡是我国古代数学家<a href="https://baike.baidu.com/item/%E5%BC%A0%E4%B8%98%E5%BB%BA/10246238">张丘建</a>在《算经》一书中提出的数学问题：鸡翁一值钱五，鸡母一值钱三，鸡雏三值钱一。百钱买百鸡，问鸡翁、鸡母、鸡雏各几何？翻译成现代文是：公鸡5元一只，母鸡3元一只，小鸡1元三只，用100块钱买一百只鸡，问公鸡、母鸡、小鸡各有多少只？</p></blockquote><p>看到这个我脑海想到的就是解方程，设置三个未知数</p>]]></content>
      
      
      
    </entry>
    
    
    
    <entry>
      <title>python小案例（三）</title>
      <link href="/posts/1/"/>
      <url>/posts/1/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<link rel="stylesheet" class="aplayer-secondary-style-marker" href="\assets\css\APlayer.min.css"><script src="\assets\js\APlayer.min.js" class="aplayer-secondary-script-marker"></script><h3 id="1-寻找水仙花数"><a href="#1-寻找水仙花数" class="headerlink" title="1.寻找水仙花数"></a>1.寻找水仙花数</h3><blockquote><p>解释：水仙花数也被称为超完全数字不变数、自恋数、自幂数、阿姆斯特朗数，它是一个3位数，该数字每个位上数字的立方之和正好等于它本身，例如：$153=1^3+5^3+3^3$</p></blockquote><p>这里的关键就是如何将个位、十位和百位表示出来</p><blockquote><p>[!NOTE]</p><ul><li>//的作用是向下取整，%是取余数</li><li>限定遍历三位数</li><li>注意<code>=</code>和<code>==</code>的区别，后者才是数学中的等于的意思，前者是变量赋值的意思</li></ul></blockquote><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">print</span>(<span class="string">&quot;\t求水仙花数&quot;</span>)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># // 运算符是向下取整的意思，这里是要把个位、十位和百位表示出来</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 遍历所有三位数</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">for</span> num <span class="keyword">in</span> <span class="built_in">range</span>(<span class="number">100</span>,<span class="number">1000</span>) :</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment"># 取余求个位上的数</span></span><br><span class="line">    a = num % <span class="number">10</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment"># 向下取整求百位上的数</span></span><br><span class="line">    b = num // <span class="number">100</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment"># 两者结合求十位上的数字</span></span><br><span class="line">    c = ( num // <span class="number">10</span> ) % <span class="number">10</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">if</span> num == a**<span class="number">3</span> + b**<span class="number">3</span> +c**<span class="number">3</span> :   </span><br><span class="line">        <span class="built_in">print</span>(num)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="2-猜数字游戏"><a href="#2-猜数字游戏" class="headerlink" title="2.猜数字游戏"></a>2.猜数字游戏</h3><blockquote><p>解释：程序在一个范围内（例如 1 到 100）随机生成一个数字，用户来猜测这个数字，程序根据用户猜测的数字给出提示（大了、小了还是猜对了）</p><p>[!NOTE]</p><ul><li>调用random库随机生成一个数</li><li>利用<code>while</code>循环和<code>if···else</code>结构持续输入和反馈</li></ul></blockquote><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">print</span>(<span class="string">&quot;\t欢迎来到数字猜谜游戏&quot;</span>)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 调用random库的随机生成整数的函数</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> random</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 随机生成一个在1到99的数字</span></span><br><span class="line">a = random.randint(<span class="number">1</span>,<span class="number">100</span>)</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">while</span> <span class="literal">True</span> :</span><br><span class="line">        user = <span class="built_in">int</span>(<span class="built_in">input</span>(<span class="string">&quot;请输入你的答案：&quot;</span>))</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">if</span> user&lt;a:</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="built_in">print</span>(<span class="string">&quot;太小啦&quot;</span>)</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">elif</span> user&gt;a:</span><br><span class="line">            <span class="built_in">print</span>(<span class="string">&quot;太大啦&quot;</span>)   </span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">else</span>: </span><br><span class="line">            <span class="built_in">print</span>(<span class="string">&quot;恭喜你猜对啦&quot;</span>)                           </span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>这里有三个分支，对应不同的情况</p>]]></content>
      
      
