    <entry>
      <title>python小案例（二）</title>
      <link href="/posts/27903/"/>
      <url>/posts/27903/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<link rel="stylesheet" class="aplayer-secondary-style-marker" href="\assets\css\APlayer.min.css"><script src="\assets\js\APlayer.min.js" class="aplayer-secondary-script-marker"></script><h2 id="海伦公式求三角形面积"><a href="#海伦公式求三角形面积" class="headerlink" title="海伦公式求三角形面积"></a>海伦公式求三角形面积</h2><p>提示：<img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/tingshuo-yiqing/PicGo-tuchuang/img/20241231193046960.png" alt=""></p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">print</span>(<span class="string">&quot;\t输入三条边长求面积&quot;</span>)</span><br><span class="line">a = <span class="built_in">float</span>(<span class="built_in">input</span>(<span class="string">&quot;请输入第一条：&quot;</span>))</span><br><span class="line">b = <span class="built_in">float</span>(<span class="built_in">input</span>(<span class="string">&quot;请输入第二条：&quot;</span>))</span><br><span class="line">c = <span class="built_in">float</span>(<span class="built_in">input</span>(<span class="string">&quot;请输入第三条：&quot;</span>))</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 条件判断如果用户输入的不符合三角形定义则会输出0</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">if</span> a+b&lt;=c <span class="keyword">or</span> a+c&lt;=b <span class="keyword">or</span> b+c&lt;=a :</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="built_in">print</span>(<span class="string">&quot;请输入正确的三条边关系&quot;</span>)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">else</span> :</span><br><span class="line">    p = (a+b+c)/<span class="number">2</span></span><br><span class="line">    var = p*(p-a)*(p-b)*(p-c)</span><br><span class="line">    area = var**<span class="number">0.5</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment"># 因为可能会出现无限小数的情况所以用round()来进行保留小数</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="built_in">print</span>(<span class="string">&quot;该三角形的面积为：&quot;</span>,<span class="built_in">round</span>(area,<span class="number">2</span>))</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><blockquote><p>[!NOTE]</p><ul><li>round()函数的特点是四舍五入，返回一个浮点数</li><li>格式化：用’{:.nf}’.format(),n是要保留的位数这种方式不只限于数字，能格式化多个值</li></ul></blockquote><h2 id="九九乘法表"><a href="#九九乘法表" class="headerlink" title="九九乘法表"></a>九九乘法表</h2><p>这里主要考察循环和print()的理解</p><p>提示：这里要嵌套，因为1要乘1，然后2要乘1到2，3要乘1到3，一直乘到81个</p><p>这里简单了解一下函数的定义<br><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title function_">function_name</span>(<span class="params">parameters</span>):</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment"># 函数体</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment"># 这里是函数的具体逻辑</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> result</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><blockquote><ul><li><code>def</code>,即define对什么下定义的意思</li><li><code>function_name</code>函数名,尽量命名的合理一点，且返回的括号里填函数名</li><li><code>parameters</code>,参数</li><li>返回是不需要：的</li></ul></blockquote><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 定义一个相乘的函数</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title function_">caculate</span>(<span class="params">i,j</span>):</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> i*j</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># for循环</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">for</span> i <span class="keyword">in</span> <span class="built_in">range</span>(<span class="number">1</span>,<span class="number">10</span>):</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">for</span> j <span class="keyword">in</span> <span class="built_in">range</span>(<span class="number">1</span>,i+<span class="number">1</span>):</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="comment"># 这里就体现了格式化f&#x27;&#x27;的作用，如果不格式化的化，输出的全都是结果</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="built_in">print</span>(<span class="string">f&#x27;<span class="subst">&#123;j&#125;</span> x <span class="subst">&#123;i&#125;</span> =&#x27;</span>,caculate(i,j))</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>效果如下：</p><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/tingshuo-yiqing/PicGo-tuchuang/img/20250101212656587.png" style="zoom: 25%;" /></p><p>这里与我们所想的结果还差了点意思因为没有形成那种我们常见的<strong>三角递减结构</strong>，这是因为我们没有换行所致的</p><blockquote><p>在 <code>print()</code> 函数中，<code>end</code> 参数用于指定在输出内容结尾处添加的字符。默认情况下，<code>print()</code> 函数在输出内容之后会添加一个换行符 <code>\n</code>，这就是为什么我们的打印都是一行一行输出的</p></blockquote><p>在这里我们要改变<code>end=</code>参数，把<code>\n</code>去掉换成<code>end=\t&#39;&#39;</code>试试</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 定义一个相乘的函数</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title function_">caculate</span>(<span class="params">i,j</span>):</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> i*j</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># for循环</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">for</span> i <span class="keyword">in</span> <span class="built_in">range</span>(<span class="number">1</span>,<span class="number">10</span>):</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">for</span> j <span class="keyword">in</span> <span class="built_in">range</span>(<span class="number">1</span>,i+<span class="number">1</span>):</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="comment"># 这里就体现了格式化f&#x27;&#x27;的作用，如果不格式化的化，输出的全都是结果</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="built_in">print</span>(<span class="string">f&#x27;<span class="subst">&#123;j&#125;</span> x <span class="subst">&#123;i&#125;</span> =&#x27;</span>,caculate(i,j),end=<span class="string">&#x27;\t&#x27;</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/tingshuo-yiqing/PicGo-tuchuang/img/20250101220323240.png" alt=""></p><p>发现还是有问题，因为我们<strong>只是控制了同行输出的格式</strong>(因为屏幕大小原因不然是不会换行的，<strong>这里应该只有特别长一行</strong>)，所以每行结束时()，还需要一个换行符来确保形成多行</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 定义一个相乘的函数</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title function_">calculate</span>(<span class="params">i, j</span>):</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> i * j</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># for循环</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">for</span> i <span class="keyword">in</span> <span class="built_in">range</span>(<span class="number">1</span>, <span class="number">10</span>):</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">for</span> j <span class="keyword">in</span> <span class="built_in">range</span>(<span class="number">1</span>, i + <span class="number">1</span>):</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="comment"># 这里就体现了格式化&#x27;f&#x27;的作用，如果不格式化的话，输出的全都是结果</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="built_in">print</span>(<span class="string">f&quot;<span class="subst">&#123;j&#125;</span> x <span class="subst">&#123;i&#125;</span> = <span class="subst">&#123;calculate(i, j)&#125;</span>&quot;</span>, end=<span class="string">&#x27;\t&#x27;</span>)</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="built_in">print</span>()</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/tingshuo-yiqing/PicGo-tuchuang/img/20250101215949702.png" style="zoom: 33%;" /></p><p>这就是最终效果了</p>]]></content>
      
      
      
