      <title>python小案例（一）</title>
      <link href="/posts/12351/"/>
      <url>/posts/12351/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<link rel="stylesheet" class="aplayer-secondary-style-marker" href="\assets\css\APlayer.min.css"><script src="\assets\js\APlayer.min.js" class="aplayer-secondary-script-marker"></script><h2 id="python简单的运用"><a href="#python简单的运用" class="headerlink" title="python简单的运用"></a>python简单的运用</h2><h3 id="1-利用math库求圆的周长和面积"><a href="#1-利用math库求圆的周长和面积" class="headerlink" title="1.利用math库求圆的周长和面积"></a>1.利用math库求圆的周长和面积</h3><p>我们需要导入pi（就是派），然后再利用公式进行计算<br>为了更好的学习，我们必须掌握一定的词汇量，所以我们的变量都用英语全称来写<br>越早熟悉越好</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="string">&#x27;&#x27;&#x27;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">半径：radius</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">直径：diameter</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">周长；perimeter</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">面积；area</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">Author: ting shuo</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">Date:2024-12-29</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">&#x27;&#x27;&#x27;</span></span><br><span class="line">form math <span class="keyword">import</span> pi</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>导入完了以后，我们需要用户输入，python处理，再输出</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">from</span> math <span class="keyword">import</span> pi</span><br><span class="line">radius = <span class="built_in">float</span>(<span class="built_in">input</span>(<span class="string">&quot;请输入半径：&quot;</span>))</span><br><span class="line">perimeter = <span class="number">2</span>*pi*radius</span><br><span class="line">area = pi*radius**<span class="number">2</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">print</span>(<span class="string">&quot;圆的周长为：&quot;</span>,<span class="built_in">round</span>(perimeter,<span class="number">2</span>))</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">print</span>(<span class="string">&quot;圆的面积为：&quot;</span>,<span class="built_in">round</span>(area,<span class="number">2</span>))</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><blockquote><p>[!IMPORTANT]</p><p>因为input函数会使输入的参数变为字符串，不能直接进行计算<br>所以要记得将其转化为浮点数或整数</p></blockquote><p>效果如下：</p><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/tingshuo-yiqing/PicGo-tuchuang/img/20241229184326150.png" style="zoom:50%;" /></p><h3 id="2-阶乘的计算"><a href="#2-阶乘的计算" class="headerlink" title="2.阶乘的计算"></a>2.阶乘的计算</h3><p>想到阶乘我们的第一反应是<code>1x2x3x4···(n-1)xn</code>即<code>迭代</code>，所以我们也利用这个定义转化成python代码</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">print</span>(<span class="string">&quot;\t阶乘的计算&quot;</span>)</span><br><span class="line">num = <span class="built_in">int</span>(<span class="built_in">input</span>(<span class="string">&quot;请输入正整数：&quot;</span>))</span><br><span class="line">result = <span class="number">1</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">for</span> i <span class="keyword">in</span> <span class="built_in">range</span>(<span class="number">1</span>,num+<span class="number">1</span>):</span><br><span class="line">    result *= i</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">print</span>(result)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>这里需要注意的是print()的缩进，不同的缩进结果是不同的</p><p>还有一种方法是进行<code>函数的封装</code>：</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title function_">factorial_calculate</span>(<span class="params">n</span>):</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment"># 函数体</span></span><br><span class="line">    result = <span class="number">1</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">for</span> i <span class="keyword">in</span> <span class="built_in">range</span>(<span class="number">1</span>,n+<span class="number">1</span>):</span><br><span class="line">        result *= i</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> result</span><br><span class="line">num = <span class="built_in">int</span>(<span class="built_in">input</span>(<span class="string">&quot;请输入正整数：&quot;</span>))</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 这里调用函数时就不要用参数n了用用户输入的值</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">print</span>(factorial_calculate(num))</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><blockquote><p>[!IMPORTANT]</p><ul><li>注意n只是一个参数，我们在打印时是不要打印n的，应该打印输入的那个变量</li><li>注意return的缩进</li></ul></blockquote><p>因为在python的标准库math中含有阶乘factorial()，所以我们也可以直接<code>调用math库</code>来计算</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> math</span><br><span class="line">num = <span class="built_in">int</span>(<span class="built_in">input</span>(<span class="string">&quot;请输入正整数：&quot;</span>))</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">print</span>(math.factorial(num))</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>还有一种<code>递归recursive</code>的方法和定义函数有点像，递归是一种在函数中调用自身来解决问题的编程技巧</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title function_">function_recursive</span>(<span class="params">n</span>):</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">if</span> n == <span class="number">0</span>:</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="number">1</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">else</span>:</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">return</span> n*function_recursive(n-<span class="number">1</span>) <span class="comment"># 在内部调用自己</span></span><br><span class="line">num = <span class="built_in">int</span>(<span class="built_in">input</span>(<span class="string">&quot;请输入正整数：&quot;</span>))</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">print</span>(function_recursive(num))</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>注意<strong>函数中不同分支不同情况要分别return</strong>，以上这些方法都可以求阶乘</p><h3 id="3-简单的逻辑翻译"><a href="#3-简单的逻辑翻译" class="headerlink" title="3.简单的逻辑翻译"></a>3.简单的逻辑翻译</h3><p>即将给出的条件翻译过来</p><p>如：找到2000年至3200年（包含3200）中的所有<strong>可被7整除但不能被5整除的所有数字，得到的数字用分号隔开</strong>，打印<strong>一行</strong>出来。</p><blockquote><p>条件一：所有</p><p>条件二：可被7整除但不能被5整除<br>条件三：一行</p></blockquote><p>所以我们就要把条件转换为编程语言，一看到除法就要想到取余符号<code>%</code>，一行就是不换行<code>end=&quot;&quot;</code><br><code>end=&quot;&quot;</code>是<code>print()</code>的参数主要用于决定输出后是什么，<code>end=</code>默认是换行符<code>\n</code></p><blockquote><p>[!TIP]</p><p>这里我们会用到<strong>格式化字符串字面量</strong>也就是<code>f&quot;&quot;</code>,这里f就是格式format的意思</p></blockquote><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">#利用end=&quot;,&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">for</span> i <span class="keyword">in</span> <span class="built_in">range</span>(<span class="number">2000</span>,<span class="number">3201</span>):</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">if</span> i%<span class="number">7</span> == <span class="number">0</span> <span class="keyword">and</span> i%<span class="number">5</span> i= <span class="number">0</span>:</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="built_in">print</span>(<span class="string">f&quot;<span class="subst">&#123;i&#125;</span>&quot;</span>,end=<span class="string">&quot;,&quot;</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">#利用f&quot;&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">for</span> i <span class="keyword">in</span> <span class="built_in">range</span>(<span class="number">2000</span>,<span class="number">3201</span>):</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">if</span> i%<span class="number">7</span> == <span class="number">0</span> <span class="keyword">and</span> i%<span class="number">5</span> i= <span class="number">0</span>:</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="built_in">print</span>(<span class="string">f&quot;<span class="subst">&#123;i&#125;</span>,&quot;</span>end=<span class="string">&quot;&quot;</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>两者结果一致效果如下：</p><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/tingshuo-yiqing/PicGo-tuchuang/img/20241230234044708.png" style="zoom:50%;" /></p><p>这两种方法都差不多，还有一种更快的方法<br><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">#列表推导式，要快的多</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">print</span>(<span class="string">&#x27;,&#x27;</span>.join(<span class="built_in">str</span>(i) <span class="keyword">for</span> i <span class="keyword">in</span> <span class="built_in">range</span>(<span class="number">2000</span>, <span class="number">3201</span>) <span class="keyword">if</span> i % <span class="number">7</span> == <span class="number">0</span> <span class="keyword">and</span> i % <span class="number">5</span>!= <span class="number">0</span>))</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>]]></content>
      
      
